    "causal_summary": "The zero-install fallback is silently broken: `probeHfLocal` (`auto-select.ts:435-449`) still gates hf-local selection on a Python `import sentencetransformers` probe, but the post-029 server is pure-Node with zero Python, so a normal Node-only machine fails the probe, rejects hf-local, and falls through to an error or silent cloud egress",
